The paper also discusses the use of ReLU nonlinearities, which is a common technique in deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of deep networks in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), which are both popular applications of deep learning. Finally, the paper discusses the limitations of shallow networks, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
